{"tid":949640,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[時代革命, 唔去酒店唔買保單]【投保唔使經中介】保泰人壽獲港首個虛擬保險牌","createTime":"2018-12-21T03:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T03:25:20.000Z","uid":57424,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d85306c347754e8788b598c2a65bc789e8efb637","tid":949640,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331463&d=K1xDqp88wxMF2YPk1dXPKcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=afa6cd35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331463&h=ec1706d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331463</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】保監局向保泰人壽發出本港首個虛擬保險牌照。<br />\n<br />\n保泰人壽表示，目標於明年上半年正式營運，以網上渠道銷售人壽及醫療保險產品，客戶可自行投保，毋需中介人參與。<br />\n<br />\n保監局則表示，目前正審視其餘多個申請，準備就緒後便會再發出牌照。<br />\n<br />\n保監局於去年9月推出快速通道，加快處理以全數碼分銷渠道的保險公司牌照申請，但償付能力及資本等監管要求則與現行的一致。<br />\n<br />\nonline 買除時好過搵人買, 點解仲要搵人買, 除非有得深入了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc15c1460594742198307171d5c97f6c70842b8","tid":949640,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"驚有愛滋病，不了"},{"pid":"cf1f9596d472c536a1cf4dfef80a806c64f3ba70","tid":949640,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc15c1460594742198307171d5c97f6c70842b8","tid":949640,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"驚有愛滋病，不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"咁記得成世好好保護你條J"},{"pid":"41c8c79780c5f1d5dfc340905c395cb721bdb636","tid":949640,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1f9596d472c536a1cf4dfef80a806c64f3ba70","tid":949640,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc15c1460594742198307171d5c97f6c70842